# =============================================================================
# Arctis — `.gitleaksignore` (fingerprint overrides)
# =============================================================================
# PRIMARY: Path-based suppression for whole directories lives in `.gitleaks.toml`
# (`[allowlist].paths` for reports/, tests/, input/, output/). That is CI-stable when
# line numbers change and is the preferred mechanism for this repository.
#
# THIS FILE: Per-finding fingerprints (Gitleaks v8+). Use for:
#   - Redundant audit trail for known false positives (same as path rules), and/or
#   - Any future false positive that appears OUTSIDE the allowlisted paths.
#
# Format (typical dir / unstaged scan, no commit prefix):
#   path/to/file.ext:rule-id:line
# List both separators so Windows (\) and Linux (/) match deterministically.
# =============================================================================

